data.description: Looking For A Spacious & Well-Maintained Home To Call Your Own?  Look No Further ! This Large One Family Is Situated Right In Prestigious Maspeth Plateau And It Has Plenty Of Character & Tones Of Charm! The Upper Level Features Three Large Bedrooms & A Full Bathroom. The Main Floor Offers Filled With Natural Light Living Room With Gas Fireplace, Formal Dining Room, Eat In Kitchen & Home Office. Moreover, You Will Find An Additional Space In A Full Finished Basement.  You Will Also Love The The Large Private Yard With A Patio And A Private Parking. First Class Location, Close To Virtually Everything: Multiple Bus Lines, Dining, Groceries, Schools And Major Highways.
